name: Penalties
text:
[§451A-19]  Penalties.  Any person who violates this chapter shall be fined not more than $500 or imprisoned not more than ninety days, or both. [L 1969, c 205, pt of §1]
 
Cross References
 
  Classification of offense and authorized punishment, see §§701-107, 706-640, and 706-663.
